<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Simple Map</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Muli:400,300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  </head>

  <body>

    <h1>Hyde Park Crime Mapping</h1>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-5" id="selections">
        <div class="col-sm-10 text-left">
         <%= form_for(search_path, :method => :post, 
          :html => {:class => "form-inline", :name => "form", :id => "form"}) do |f| %>

          
            <div class="form-group">
            <%= label_tag(:address, params[:address], class: "sr-only") %>
            <%= f.text_field_tag(:address, nil, placeholder: "ADDRESS", class: "ipt") %>

            <%= label_tag(:key_words, params[:key_words], class: "sr-only") %>
            <%= f.text_field_tag(:key_words, nil, placeholder: "KEY WORDS", class: "ipt") %>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <div class="input-group date" id="timepickerstart" name="start_time">
                <%= f.text_field_tag(:start, nil, class: "form-control") %>
                <span class="input-group-addon">
                  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <div class="input-group date" id="timepickerend" name="end_time">
                <%= f.text_field_tag(:end, nil, class: "form-control") %>
                <span class="input-group-addon">
                  <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= button_tag("SUBMIT", type: "button", id: "submit", class: ["btn", "btn-default"]) %>
            <div id="notes"></div>
          </div>

        <% end %> 
        </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-7" id="map"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <footer class="working">
          <span id="footer-toggle">NOTE</span>
          <div id="footer" style="display:none;">
            Because of Google Map API's limit on the number of queries made per second, some of the bigger search results that span more than a couple of day's worth of stuff will take a couple of seconds to fully load (there's actually a suprising number of entries for a period of say, a week). 
          </div>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyAbZbQ1OXo5JR2T3fcuZTfwipr772I-VyE&callback=initMap"
    async defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
